Phan mem node to do
app: main file
public: chua cac resource tinh cho client truy cap
views: chua cac file template cho client
api: tao api de doc du lieu
config: luu tru thong tin ve database

app: initialize, khoi tao port, cau hinh de su dung cac middleware + tai nguyen tinh, doc kieu du lieu tu nguoi dung gui len la kieu json, doc kieu urlencoded
	initialize app: gan express(vi express is a module to create application, and also a function
	setup middleware: cau hinh route den tai nguyen tinh, lay cac tai nguyen tinh tu file public (phai create virtual path prefix(where the path does not actually exist in the file system))
	setup views: load template engine ejs using view engine
	setup route:  setup trang chu :/

api: tao schema du lieu roi chia ra cho app.js
trong app.js: thiet lap ket noi vs database
